            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金利食安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7743:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7743\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7743-TW</a>)近5分K跌速3.41%，06日11:23報32.55元，成交456張，今日漲幅為5.51％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金利食安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7743:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7743\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7743-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌0.48%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+974 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,000 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-26 張</li> </ul></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
